Hind
limbs more robust than forelimbs, tibia relatively short (CrusL/SVL 
0.11
), covered dorsally with granular scales; ventral hind limb scales flat, larger than dorsals; enlarged femoral scales absent, femoral pores absent; digits short, subdigital lamellae of pes transversely expanded proximal to inflected joints, digits narrow distal to joints; count of subdigital lamellae on pes: I(
10
), II(
11
), III(
13
), IV(
15
), V(
13
